sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Device
    participant Server
    participant DB as DeviceRecordDB
    participant Audit

    Device->>Server: RegistrationRequest(CRPs, policy params)
    Server->>Server: Train surrogate + tune threshold
    Server->>DB: Store identity tag, model params, policies
    Server->>Audit: registration.enroll(ok)
    Server-->>Device: RegistrationResult(identity_tag, matrix_set)

    Device->>Server: Auth request(device_id)
    Server->>DB: Load record + enforce lockout/query limits
    Server->>Server: Build signed challenge
    Server->>Audit: auth.issue_challenge(ok/fail)
    Server-->>Device: AuthenticationChallenge(server_message)

    Device->>Device: Verify challenge authenticity/freshness
    Device->>Device: Derive PUF response bits
    Device->>Device: Matrix encrypt response
    Device-->>Server: AuthenticationReply(device_message)

    Server->>Server: Verify reply MAC + nonce freshness
    Server->>Server: Decrypt response bits
    Server->>Server: Optional ECC/fuzzy recovery
    Server->>Server: Compare hamming ratio vs threshold

    alt Authentication success
        Server->>Server: Derive PUF session key
        Server->>DB: Update authenticated state
        Server->>Audit: auth.verify_reply(ok)
        Server-->>Device: AuthenticationResult(success, session_key ref)
    else Authentication failure
        Server->>DB: Increment failed attempts / set lockout
        Server->>Audit: auth.verify_reply(fail)
        Server-->>Device: AuthenticationResult(fail, reason)
    end

    opt Large payload hybrid mode
        Server->>Server: Derive key via PUF challenge set
        Server-->>Device: AES-GCM payload + key challenges
        Device->>Device: Re-derive key + decrypt payload
    end
